mysql_query: SELECT * FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (IFNULL(CTW,0) + IFNULL(CTF,0) + IFNULL(CTU,0) + IFNULL(CTA,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CTW FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CTF FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) B ON P.PLAYER_ID = B.ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CTU FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CTA FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) D ON P.PLAYER_ID = D.ID) H WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT!= 0

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ) T WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS CROSS JOIN PLAYERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) T WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) AS Z WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID,1,0))+SUM(IF(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0))+SUM(IF(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0))+SUM(IF(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0))) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) AS TEMP WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT

SELECT * FROM( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS CROSS JOIN PLAYERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) TEMP WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS PLAYER_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS PLAYER_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS PLAYER_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS PLAYER_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID , A.PLAYER_NAME , SUM(A.PLAYER_ID=B.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(A.PLAYER_ID=B.FR_OPEN) + SUM(A.PLAYER_ID=B.US_OPEN) + SUM(A.PLAYER_ID=B.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.WIMBLEDON OR A.PLAYER_ID=B.FR_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID=B.US_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID=B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS A INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT B.PLAYER PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT A.PLAYER, COUNT(A.PLAYER) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A GROUP BY A.PLAYER) B LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON B.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) B INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON B.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT DISTINCT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(IF(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0))) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS T JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON T.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS T, PLAYERS AS P WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.AU_OPEN =P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT!=0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.AU_OPEN =P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT!=0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN =P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT!=0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN =P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN =P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT!=0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) OR (P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) OR (P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) OR (P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) AS T2 ON(T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY PLAYER_ID DESC

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT !=0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,B.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(GS_CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GS_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS GS_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS GS_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS GS_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, C.CT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS B INNER JOIN ( SELECT ID, COUNT(*) AS CT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A GROUP BY ID ) C ON B.PLAYER_ID = C.ID

SELECT C.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT C.PLAYER_ID PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID

SELECT D.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(D.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT C.WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT C.FR_OPEN, COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT C.US_OPEN, COUNT(C.US_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT C.AU_OPEN, COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY C.AU_OPEN) AS D JOIN PLAYERS P ON D.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY D.PLAYER_ID

SELECT MAT AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS MAT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS MAT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS MAT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS MAT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C )A JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.MAT = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN)+ SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,SUM( CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, ( SUM( CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) + SUM( CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) + SUM( CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) + SUM( CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.GRAND_SLAMS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.GRAND_SLAMS GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS NUM_WINS JOIN PLAYERS P ON NUM_WINS.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN B.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN B.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN B.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN B.AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS B GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+ CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+ CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+ CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 3

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID IN (C.WIMBLEDON, C.FR_OPEN, C.US_OPEN, C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )T JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.CHAMP GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.WIN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING COUNT(T.WIN)>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P1.PLAYER_ID, P1.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 JOIN PLAYERS P1 ON C1.AU_OPEN = P1.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P2.PLAYER_ID, P2.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C2 JOIN PLAYERS P2 ON C2.WIMBLEDON = P2.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P3.PLAYER_ID, P3.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C3 JOIN PLAYERS P3 ON C3.FR_OPEN = P3.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P4.PLAYER_ID, P4.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C4 JOIN PLAYERS P4 ON C4.US_OPEN = P4.PLAYER_ID) ALLWINNERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS AWARDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS AWARDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS AWARDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS AWARDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TEMP1 JOIN PLAYERS ON TEMP1.AWARDS = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.WIN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS F ON P.PLAYER_ID = F.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS U ON P.PLAYER_ID = U.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.AU_OPEN) T GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( (CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( IF(C.WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) ) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID THEN 1.0 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID THEN 1.0 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID THEN 1.0 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID THEN 1.0 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON 1=1 GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) <> 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C, PLAYERS P GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPIONSHIP, P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION SELECT FR_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP, P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION SELECT US_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP, P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION SELECT AU_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP, P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ) A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT * FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) T GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID IN (WIMBLEDON, FR_OPEN, US_OPEN, AU_OPEN) GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID IN (WIMBLEDON, FR_OPEN, US_OPEN, AU_OPEN) GROUP BY 2,1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TOT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT S2.PLAYER_ID, S2.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(S1.WIMBLEDON) AS TOT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS S1, PLAYERS S2 WHERE S2.PLAYER_ID=S1.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT S2.PLAYER_ID, S2.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(S1.FR_OPEN) AS TOT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS S1, PLAYERS S2 WHERE S2.PLAYER_ID=S1.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT S2.PLAYER_ID, S2.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(S1.US_OPEN) AS TOT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS S1, PLAYERS S2 WHERE S2.PLAYER_ID=S1.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT S2.PLAYER_ID, S2.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(S1.AU_OPEN) AS TOT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS S1, PLAYERS S2 WHERE S2.PLAYER_ID=S1.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2) OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TOTAL) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS TOTAL FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS TOTAL FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS TOTAL FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS TOTAL FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) AS T GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) CHMP ON PLAYER_ID = CHMP.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) A GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ) AS T WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT >= 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0 ORDER BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) > 0 ORDER BY 3 DESC

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ORDER BY 3 DESC

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(X.GS) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) X JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=X.GS GROUP BY X.GS

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM((IF(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID,1,0)+IF(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0)+IF(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0)+IF(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0)) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING (SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN)) > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,SUM(CNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) CNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) CNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) CNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) CNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME ) R GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PP.PLAYER_ID, PP.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PP.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.US_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME) PP GROUP BY PP.PLAYER_ID, PP.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT SUB1.PLAYER_ID, SUB2.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SUB1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS SUB2 ON SUB1.PLAYER_ID = SUB2.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT T.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, T.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME) AS T GROUP BY T.PLAYER_ID, T.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT T2.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, T3.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME ,T2.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )T1 GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID) T2 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS T3 ON T2.PLAYER_ID=T3.PLAYER_ID

SELECT TMP.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(NUM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) TMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON TMP.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT TMP.PLAYER_ID, TMP.PLAYER_NAME, (WSUM + FSUM + USUM + ASUM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS WSUM, SUM( CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS FSUM, SUM( CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS USUM, SUM( CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS ASUM FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY P.PLAYER_ID) AS TMP

SELECT U.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) U JOIN PLAYERS P ON U.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY U.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P1.PLAYER_ID, P1.PLAYER_NAME, COALESCE(W1.W, 0) + COALESCE(F1.F, 0) + COALESCE(U1.U, 0) + COALESCE(A1.A, 0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P1 LEFT JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS P1, COUNT(*) AS W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) AS W1 ON P1.PLAYER_ID =W1.P1 LEFT JOIN (SELECT FR_OPEN AS F1, COUNT(*) AS F FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) AS F1 ON P1.PLAYER_ID =F1.F1 LEFT JOIN (SELECT US_OPEN AS U1, COUNT(*) AS U FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) AS U1 ON P1.PLAYER_ID =U1.U1 LEFT JOIN (SELECT AU_OPEN AS A1, COUNT(*) AS A FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) AS A1 ON P1.PLAYER_ID =A1.A1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT CHAMPIONSHIP AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT CHAMPIONSHIP, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR , WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR , FR_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR , US_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR , AU_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )A GROUP BY 1 )B JOIN PLAYERS P ON PLAYER_ID = CHAMPIONSHIP

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( IF(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( IF(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TOTAL_WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER , COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS TOTAL_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER , COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS TOTAL_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER , COUNT(US_OPEN) AS TOTAL_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER , COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS TOTAL_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER ) T1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T1.PLAYER GROUP BY T1.PLAYER

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+ SUM( PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN )+ SUM( PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN )+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN (SELECT WINNER, COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A GROUP BY WINNER ) B ON P.PLAYER_ID = B.WINNER

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIM) + SUM(FRENCH) + SUM(US) + SUM(AUS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS WIM, CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS FRENCH, CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS US, CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS AUS FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) X GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH BASE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TOURNAMENT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN BASE AS B ON P.PLAYER_ID = B.TOURNAMENT GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CET AS(SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CET C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) CN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) CN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) CN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) CN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER=PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER

WITH CTE AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT DESC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GRAND_SLAM_WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE1 ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE1.GRAND_SLAM_WINNER GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CHAMPIONSHIPSDETAILS AS (SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), CHAMPIONSHIPSSUMMARY AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID ,COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPSDETAILS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,CS.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPSSUMMARY CS ON CS.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CHAMPIONSHIPS_TRANSPOSED AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, 'WIMBLEDON' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'FRENCH OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'US OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'AUSTRALIAN OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(TOURNAMENT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS_TRANSPOSED C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH T1 AS ( (SELECT YEAR , WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT YEAR , FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT YEAR , US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT YEAR , AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) ), T2 AS ( SELECT GAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 GROUP BY GAME) SELECT T2.GAME AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, T2.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T2 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T2.GAME = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN T1 USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2

WITH T1 AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), T2 AS (SELECT *, WINNER AS PLAYER_ID FROM T1) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B. PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T2 A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT TEMP.TOURNAMENT AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP JOIN PLAYERS ON TEMP.TOURNAMENT = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TOURNAMENT

WITH TST AS( SELECT ID, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) AS T1 GROUP BY ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TST LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON ID=PLAYER_ID

WITH TITLES AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P RIGHT JOIN TITLES AS T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.CHAMPION GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH WINS AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT W.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINS W INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=W.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY W.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH WINNERS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(W.WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNERS W LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON W.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY W.WINNER

WITH ALLWINS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN ALLWINS A WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = A.WINS GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH C AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), SUMMARY AS (SELECT ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C GROUP BY ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, S.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN SUMMARY S ON P.PLAYER_ID = S.ID

WITH C1 AS (SELECT P.* ,C.WIMBLEDON ,C.FR_OPEN ,C.US_OPEN ,C.AU_OPEN FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) SELECT PLAYER_ID ,PLAYER_NAME ,SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON,1,0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN,1,0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN,1,0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN,1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C1 GROUP BY 1

WITH CHAMP_LONG AS ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMP_LONG AS CL ON CL.CHAMP_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT >= 1

WITH CORE AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS T1 INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS T1 INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS T1 INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS T1 INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CORE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.GAMES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CTE AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CTE.ID AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(CTE.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT PLAYER FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )A UNION ALL ( SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) UNION ALL ( SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) UNION ALL ( SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) ) SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE X INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER,PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE_ALL AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CTE_ALL.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE_ALL INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE_ALL.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 3

WITH GET_COMBINED AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN GET_COMBINED ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = GET_COMBINED.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

WITH PID AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) C1 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PL.PLAYER_NAME, P.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PID P JOIN PLAYERS PL ON PL.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH SUB AS (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GRAND_SLAM, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM, FR_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM, US_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM, AU_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(SUB.WINNER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN SUB ON P.PLAYER_ID = SUB.WINNER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN T USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS LEFT JOIN T USING (PLAYER_ID) WHERE T.PLAYER_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS(SELECT WIMBLEDON, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) NW FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON), T2 AS(SELECT FR_OPEN, COUNT(FR_OPEN) NF FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN), T3 AS(SELECT US_OPEN, COUNT(US_OPEN) NU FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN), T4 AS(SELECT AU_OPEN, COUNT(AU_OPEN) NA FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, IFNULL(T1.NW, 0) + IFNULL(T2.NF, 0)+IFNULL(T3.NU,0)+IFNULL(T4.NA,0) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN T1 ON T1.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN T2 ON T2.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN T3 ON T3.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN T4 ON T4.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS RACE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS RACE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS RACE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS RACE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT RACE AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.RACE = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.RACE, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON TEMP.SLAM = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN TEMP ON P.PLAYER_ID = TEMP.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS( (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS A JOIN TEMP AS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID

WITH TMP AS (SELECT YEAR, PLAYER_NAME, PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, PLAYER_NAME, PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, PLAYER_NAME, PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, PLAYER_NAME, PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH W AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON ), F AS ( SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN ), U AS ( SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN ), A AS ( SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ), S AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COALESCE(W.CNT, 0) + COALESCE(F.CNT, 0) + COALESCE(U.CNT, 0) + COALESCE(A.CNT, 0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN F ON P.PLAYER_ID = F.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN U ON P.PLAYER_ID = U.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT * FROM S WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH W AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS W_PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C), F AS ( SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS F_PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C), U AS ( SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS U_PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C), A AS ( SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS A_PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C) SELECT W_PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT * FROM W UNION ALL SELECT * FROM F UNION ALL SELECT * FROM U UNION ALL SELECT * FROM A) AS T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.W_PLAYER GROUP BY W_PLAYER

WITH WINNER AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT WINNER.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WINNER.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNER INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON WINNER.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY WINNER.PLAYER_ID

WITH WINNERS AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) AS WIMBLEDON, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) AS FRENCH, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) AS US, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) AS AU FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON+FRENCH+US+AU) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH WINNERS AS ( SELECT WINNER, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS COMBINED GROUP BY WINNER ) SELECT WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNERS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON WINNERS.WINNER = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

WITH WINS AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN WINS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH WINS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(W.PLAYER_WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN WINS AS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = PLAYER_WIN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH WON AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(W.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN WON AS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.ID ORDER BY C.ID DESC

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TOURNAMENTS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.TOURNAMENTS = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WINNER, COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TEMP GROUP BY WINNER) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CTE.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS CH UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS PL ON CTE.ID = PL.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ID

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT COUNT(YEAR) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(YEAR) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(YEAR) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(YEAR) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P ) AS A WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT ANS.PLAYER_ID, ANS.PLAYER_NAME, (WIMBLEDON+FR_OPEN+US_OPEN+AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT W1.PLAYER_ID, W1.PLAYER_NAME, W1.WIMBLEDON, F1.FR_OPEN, U1.US_OPEN, A1.AU_OPEN FROM (SELECT W.PLAYER_ID, W.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(W.WIMBLEDON) AS WIMBLEDON FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR AS WIMBLEDON FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) W GROUP BY W.PLAYER_ID, W.PLAYER_NAME) W1 LEFT JOIN (SELECT F.PLAYER_ID, F.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(F.FR_OPEN) AS FR_OPEN FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR AS FR_OPEN FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) F GROUP BY F.PLAYER_ID, F.PLAYER_NAME) F1 ON W1.PLAYER_ID = F1.PLAYER_ID AND W1.PLAYER_NAME = F1.PLAYER_NAME LEFT JOIN (SELECT U.PLAYER_ID, U.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(U.US_OPEN) AS US_OPEN FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR AS US_OPEN FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) U GROUP BY U.PLAYER_ID, U.PLAYER_NAME) U1 ON W1.PLAYER_ID = U1.PLAYER_ID AND W1.PLAYER_NAME = U1.PLAYER_NAME LEFT JOIN (SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.AU_OPEN) AS AU_OPEN FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.YEAR AS AU_OPEN FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) A GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME) A1 ON W1.PLAYER_ID = A1.PLAYER_ID AND W1.PLAYER_NAME = A1.PLAYER_NAME ) ANS ) ANS1 WHERE ANS1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT * FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1,2) TMP WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , ( SELECT COUNT(IF(WIMBLEDON= PLAYER_ID,1,NULL)) + COUNT(IF(FR_OPEN= PLAYER_ID,1,NULL)) + COUNT(IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,NULL)) + COUNT(IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,NULL)) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS ) A WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME) A WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT A.C AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS A JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON A.C = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.C, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS W UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(A.SLAM_COUNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS SLAM_COUNT, 'WIMBLEDON' AS EVENT_TYPE FROM PLAYERS A, CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE (A.PLAYER_ID=B.WIMBLEDON) GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME UNION SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS SLAM_COUNT, 'FRENCH OPEN' AS EVENT_TYPE FROM PLAYERS A, CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE (A.PLAYER_ID=B.FR_OPEN) GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME UNION SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS SLAM_COUNT, 'US OPEN' AS EVENT_TYPE FROM PLAYERS A, CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE (A.PLAYER_ID=B.US_OPEN) GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME UNION SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS SLAM_COUNT, 'AU OPEN' AS EVENT_TYPE FROM PLAYERS A, CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE (A.PLAYER_ID=B.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME) A GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) CHAMP JOIN PLAYERS P ON CHAMP.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 HAVING (SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) !=0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN)T , PLAYERS P WHERE T.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT A.*, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON,1,0) + IF(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN,1,0) + IF(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN,1,0) + IF(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN,1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A, CHAMPIONSHIPS B GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_NAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.ID AS PLAYER_ID , B.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(A.TITLE) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 )A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID ,A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) B ON A.PLAYER_ID =B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID ,A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) B ON A.PLAYER_ID =B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON A.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) B USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.WIN GROUP BY 1

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN) + SUM(A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN) + SUM(A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(A.W) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, ((CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) AS W FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) A GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME
