SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, TRUNCATE(A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT,0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN C.WIMBLEDON ELSE 0 END)/P.PLAYER_ID + SUM(CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN C.FR_OPEN ELSE 0 END)/P.PLAYER_ID + SUM(CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN C.US_OPEN ELSE 0 END)/P.PLAYER_ID + SUM(CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN C.AU_OPEN ELSE 0 END)/P.PLAYER_ID AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME) AS A WHERE A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(A.N) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS N FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS N FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS N FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS N FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN)) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(A.CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(COUNTS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS COUNTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS COUNTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(1) AS COUNTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(1) AS COUNTS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) B GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P2.PLAYER_ID,P1.PLAYER_NAME,P2.NUM AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P1 JOIN ( SELECT B.PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) B GROUP BY 1 ) P2 ON P1.PLAYER_ID=P2.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY 1 DESC

SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TB1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON TB1.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A,PLAYERS P WHERE A.PLAYER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER

SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )A UNION ALL ( SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) UNION ALL ( SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) UNION ALL ( SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) )X INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME , SUM(CASE WHEN B.WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN B.FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN B.US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN B.AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS , CHAMPIONSHIPS B GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT >0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME , SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON T1.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID) AS T2 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS WINS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = WINS.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 ON P.PLAYER_ID = C1.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C2 ON P.PLAYER_ID = C2.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C3 ON P.PLAYER_ID = C3.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C4 ON P.PLAYER_ID = C4.AU_OPEN)T GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS, ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A WHERE PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID=A.WIN GROUP BY A.WIN

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ((SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON ) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN ) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, YEAR FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN)) AS T GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME) TB1 WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P1 RIGHT JOIN (SELECT ID, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) S1 GROUP BY ID) S2 ON P1.PLAYER_ID = S2.ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN (SELECT ID, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) GRAND_SLAM GROUP BY ID ) GRAND_SLAM_MATCHES ON PLAYER_ID = ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C CROSS JOIN PLAYERS P GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING SUM( (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ) > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+ CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)+ IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)+ IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)+ IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM((WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) + (FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + (US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + (AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM((IF(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID,1,0)+ IF(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0) + IF(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0)+ IF(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID,1,0)))AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN= PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C, PLAYERS P GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(C.AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = W.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = W.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = W.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = W.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = W.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = W.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = W.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID,1,0) + IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0) + IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0) + IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON,1,0)+ IF(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN,1,0) + IF (PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN,1,0)+ IF(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN,1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON (PLAYER_ID= WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN OR US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID IN (WIMBLEDON, FR_OPEN, US_OPEN, AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P , CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS CROSS JOIN PLAYERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, WIMBLEDON + FR_OPEN + US_OPEN + AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, T1.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.WIMBLEDON, 1, 0)) AS WIMBLEDON, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.FR_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS FR_OPEN, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.US_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS US_OPEN, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.AU_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS AU_OPEN FROM PLAYERS T1 JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS T2 ON T2.WIMBLEDON = T1.PLAYER_ID OR T2.FR_OPEN = T1.PLAYER_ID OR T2.US_OPEN = T1.PLAYER_ID OR T2.AU_OPEN = T1.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID ) T

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, (WIN+FR+US+AU) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS WIN, SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FR, SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS US, SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AU FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS, PLAYERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME) A WHERE (WIN+FR+US+AU)>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.ID)AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID=A.ID GROUP BY PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.TITLES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.TITLES GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME HAVING COUNT(A.TITLES) > 0 ORDER BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) +SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN) +SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN) +SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON ((PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) OR (PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) OR (PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) OR (PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN)) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS P FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS P FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS P FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS P FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T JOIN PLAYERS PL ON T.P=PL.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.P

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,SUM(SLAM_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS SLAM_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(C.US_OPEN) AS SLAM_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) AS SLAM_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) AS SLAM_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 )TEST GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT!=0

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,WIM+FR+US+AU AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) WIM, SUM(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) FR, SUM(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) US, SUM(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) AU FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID )A

SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TEMP.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS TEMP ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = TEMP.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT T.WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(T.WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY T.WIMBLEDON

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.PLAYER_ID

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) T INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, T1.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.WIMBLEDON, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.FR_OPEN, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.US_OPEN, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = T2.AU_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS T1 JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS T2 ON T2.WIMBLEDON = T1.PLAYER_ID OR T2.FR_OPEN = T1.PLAYER_ID OR T2.US_OPEN = T1.PLAYER_ID OR T2.AU_OPEN = T1.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID

SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, T1.PLAYER_NAME, T1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) AS T1 WHERE T1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT T3.PLAYER_ID,T3.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT * FROM PLAYERS P JOIN (SELECT T1.GRAND_SLAMS PLAYER_ID2 FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)T1)T2 ON P.PLAYER_ID=T2.PLAYER_ID2)T3 GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT TB2.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,TB2.NUM AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WINNER,COUNT(WINNER) AS NUM FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TB GROUP BY 1) TB2 JOIN PLAYERS P ON TB2.WINNER=P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT WIN AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS A JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.WIN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT Y.PLAYER_ID, Y.PLAYER_NAME, T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS Y, (SELECT COUNT(X.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT, X.C FROM (((SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS X GROUP BY X.C) AS T WHERE Y.PLAYER_ID = T.C

WITH C AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), C1 AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT C1.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C1 INNER JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON C1.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS MATCH_NAME, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS MATCH_NAME, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS MATCH_NAME, US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS MATCH_NAME, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.PLAYER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

WITH W1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), W2 AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM W1 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, W2.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN W2 ON P.PLAYER_ID=W2.PLAYER_ID

WITH A AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.WIN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH A AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), B AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS SLAM_COUNT FROM A GROUP BY 1) SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, B.SLAM_COUNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM B JOIN PLAYERS ON B.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

WITH A AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT DISTINCT A.ID AS PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A AS A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS B ON A.ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ID

WITH ALL_CHAMPIONSHIPS AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER,YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER,YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER,YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER,YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL_CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER,PLAYER_NAME

WITH ALL_CHAMPIONSHIPS AS(SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL_CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER,PLAYER_NAME

WITH ALL_CHAMPOINSHIPS AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(A.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL_CHAMPOINSHIPS A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.ID

WITH ALL_WINS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C ) SELECT A.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL_WINS A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.WINNER GROUP BY 1,2

WITH BASE AS ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), BASE2 AS ( SELECT WINNER, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM BASE GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM BASE2 B INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON B.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH BASE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS MATCHES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS MATCHES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS MATCHES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS MATCHES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT DISTINCT MATCHES AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM BASE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON BASE.MATCHES = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CHAMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN CHAMP B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CHAMPION AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.CHAMP AS PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.CHAMP) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPION A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.CHAMP = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CHAMPIONSHIP_LIST AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID,'WIMBELDON' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID,'FR_OPEN' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID,'US_OPEN' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID,'AU_OPEN' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(1) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIP_LIST CHAMPIONSHIP_LIST WHERE PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID=CHAMPIONSHIP_LIST.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CHAMPS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CHAMPS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN, COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN, COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN, COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CHAMPS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS CHM, B.PLAYER_NAME, 1 AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.WIMBLEDON = B.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS CHM,B.PLAYER_NAME,1 AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.FR_OPEN = B.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS CHM,B.PLAYER_NAME,1 AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.US_OPEN = B.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS CHM,B.PLAYER_NAME,1 AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.AU_OPEN = B.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT CHM AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,SUM(SLAMS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPS GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CT AS ( SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.WIMBLEDON) AS VAL FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.FR_OPEN) AS VAL FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.US_OPEN) AS VAL FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.AU_OPEN) AS VAL FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME) SELECT DISTINCT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(VAL) OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CT

WITH CTE AS ( (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS C FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1) UNION ALL (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1) UNION ALL (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.US_OPEN) FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1) UNION ALL (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1) ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT C.YEAR,P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT C.YEAR,P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT C.YEAR,P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT C.YEAR,P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY PLAYER_NAME ASC

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT *,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GAME_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GAME_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GAME_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GAME_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) TB GROUP BY GAME_WON) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON GAME_WON = PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID =B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID GROUP BY ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT CTE.ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID,PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER_ID,PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME ORDER BY PLAYER_ID DESC

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ), CTE2 AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE2 A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.WINNER=PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID, 'WIMBLEDON' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID, 'FR_OPEN' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID, 'US_OPEN' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID, 'AU_OPEN' CHAMPIONSHIP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CHAMPIONSHIP) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2 ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1, 2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, 1 TOTAL FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, 1 TOTAL FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, 1 TOTAL FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, 1 TOTAL FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TOTAL) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PLAYERID , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYERID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYERID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYERID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYERID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )A GROUP BY PLAYERID ) SELECT CTE.PLAYERID AS PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.PLAYERID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C, PLAYERS P WHERE C.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.PLAYER_WON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN CTE B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_WON GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT ID PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ID,PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS MATCH_NAME, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS MATCH_NAME, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS MATCH_NAME, US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS MATCH_NAME, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON PLAYER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TITLES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.TITLES GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT TOUR AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TOUR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON TOUR = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TOUR

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS AS P USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS AS P USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, (SELECT WIMBLEDON ) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, (SELECT FR_OPEN ) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, (SELECT US_OPEN ) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, (SELECT AU_OPEN ) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR,'WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPIONSHIP',WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,'FR_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP',FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,'US_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP',US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,'AU_OPEN AS CHAMPIONSHIP',AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID =B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS CL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS CL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS CL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS CL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CL AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON CTE.CL=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CL

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(TITLE) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.TITLE = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 2

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS IDS, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN, COUNT(FR_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN, COUNT(US_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN, COUNT(AU_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, TEMP.WN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN (SELECT CTE.IDS, SUM(WIN) AS WN FROM CTE GROUP BY 1) TEMP ON TEMP.IDS = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C.ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE AS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 3

WITH CTE AS (SELECT DISTINCT CHAMPION,COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)A GROUP BY CHAMPION) SELECT CTE.CHAMPION AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CTE.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.CHAMPION=P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT ID, COUNT(ID) AS NUM FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A GROUP BY ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, NUM AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM( P.PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CTE ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) G FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SQ GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,G GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN CTE ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.CNT GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY P.PLAYER_ID DESC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CTE ON PLAYER_ID=ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYERID,COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYERID,COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYERID,COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYERID,COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYERID AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,SUM(CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYERID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYERID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR , WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID ,A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A LEFT JOIN CTE B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID WHERE B.PLAYER_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PRIZE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PRIZE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PRIZE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PRIZE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.PRIZE AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.PRIZE = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PRIZE ORDER BY CTE.PRIZE ASC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CTE ON PLAYER_ID = WINNER GROUP BY WINNER

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CHAMP) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.CHAMP=PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CHAMP

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR , WIMBLEDON AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR , FR_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR ,US_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR ,AU_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT DISTINCT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.GRANDSLAM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.GRANDSLAM = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.GRANDSLAM

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(B.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CTE B USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.PLAYER_ID)AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=CTE.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT DISTINCT WINNER, COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON AS GAME', WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN AS GAME', FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN AS GAME', US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN AS GAME', AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS A GROUP BY WINNER ) SELECT CTE.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,SUM(CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,SUM(CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,SUM(CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 ) SELECT PLAYER_ID ,PLAYER_NAME ,SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) > 0 ORDER BY 2

WITH CTE AS( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, CASE WHEN TWIM.WIMBLEDON IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS SCORE FROM PLAYERS DRV LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS TWIM ON DRV.PLAYER_ID = TWIM.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, CASE WHEN TFR.FR_OPEN IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS SCORE FROM PLAYERS DRV LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS TFR ON DRV.PLAYER_ID = TFR.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, CASE WHEN TUS.US_OPEN IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS SCORE FROM PLAYERS DRV LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS TUS ON DRV.PLAYER_ID = TUS.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, CASE WHEN TAU.AU_OPEN IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS SCORE FROM PLAYERS DRV LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS TAU ON DRV.PLAYER_ID = TAU.AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(SCORE) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING SUM(SCORE)>0

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS,CTE WHERE PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID =CTE.WINNER GROUP BY PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR AS YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR AS YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR AS YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR AS YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.WINNER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.WINNER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS(SELECT DISTINCT WINNER, COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON AS GAME', WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN AS GAME', FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN AS GAME', US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN AS GAME', AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A GROUP BY WINNER) SELECT CTE.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CTE.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS(SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) WIM, SUM(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) FR, SUM(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) US, SUM(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) AU FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, WIM+FR+US+AU AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE

WITH CTE AS(SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE(PLAYER_ID) AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE NATURAL JOIN PLAYERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE(PLAYER_ID, CHAMP) AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CHAMP AS PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.CHAMP = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT P1.PLAYER_ID, P1.PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON=P1.PLAYER_ID,1,0)+IF(FR_OPEN=P1.PLAYER_ID,1,0)+IF(US_OPEN=P1.PLAYER_ID,1,0)+IF(AU_OPEN=P1.PLAYER_ID,1,0)) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P1 ) SELECT * FROM CTE1 WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT<>0

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) ,CTE2 AS ( SELECT GRAND_SLAM AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT CTE2.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CTE2.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE2 JOIN PLAYERS P USING(PLAYER_ID)

WITH GET_PLAYER AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) ,GRP AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID , COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM GET_PLAYER GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,Q.PLAYER_NAME,GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM GRP P LEFT JOIN PLAYERS Q ON P.PLAYER_ID=Q.PLAYER_ID

WITH GRANDSLAM_CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR ,'WIMBLEDON' AS EVENT_NAME ,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR ,'FR_OPEN' AS EVENT_NAME ,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR ,'US_OPEN' AS EVENT_NAME ,US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR ,'AU_OPEN' AS EVENT_NAME ,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,COUNT(EVENT_NAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN GRANDSLAM_CTE AS C ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH GRANDSLAM_CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR ,'WIMBLEDON' AS EVENT_NAME ,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR ,'FR_OPEN' AS EVENT_NAME ,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR ,'US_OPEN' AS EVENT_NAME ,US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR ,'AU_OPEN' AS EVENT_NAME ,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME ,COUNT(EVENT_NAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN GRANDSLAM_CTE AS C ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH PLAYER_WINS AS( SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON CHAMPIONSHIPS.WIMBLEDON = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON CHAMPIONSHIPS.FR_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON CHAMPIONSHIPS.US_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON CHAMPIONSHIPS.AU_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2 ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYER_WINS P GROUP BY 1, 2

WITH SLAMZ AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS SLAMMER,1 AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS SLAMMER,1 AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS SLAMMER,1 AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS SLAMMER,1 AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT SLAMMER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TOTAL) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM SLAMZ LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON SLAMMER=PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY SLAMMER

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID,YEAR,1 AS NUM_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,YEAR,1 AS NUM_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,YEAR,1 AS NUM_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,YEAR,1 AS NUM_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(NUM_SLAMS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH T AS (SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, ((SELECT COUNT(B.WIMBLEDON) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE B.WIMBLEDON = A.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(B.FR_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE B.FR_OPEN = A.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(B.US_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE B.US_OPEN = A.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(B.AU_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE B.AU_OPEN = A.PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A ) SELECT * FROM T WHERE T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT <> 0 ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT DESC

WITH T AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.WINNER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH T AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON), T2 AS (SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN ), T3 AS (SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN ), T4 AS (SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) ,TEMP AS (SELECT * FROM T UNION ALL SELECT * FROM T2 UNION ALL SELECT * FROM T3 UNION ALL SELECT * FROM T4) SELECT TEMP.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON TEMP.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TEMP.PLAYER_ID

WITH T AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.T GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH T(ID) AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(T.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=T.ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH T0 AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN T0 ON PLAYER_ID = GRAND_SLAM GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING COUNT(PLAYER_ID) >0

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIN_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 JOIN PLAYERS ON T1.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(T1.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN T1 USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1

WITH T1 AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(US_OPEN) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON (T1.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 JOIN PLAYERS ON T1.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH T1 AS( SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(A.PLAYER_ID =B.WIMBLEDON)+SUM(A.PLAYER_ID=B.FR_OPEN)+SUM(A.PLAYER_ID=B.US_OPEN)+SUM(A.PLAYER_ID=B.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON (A.PLAYER_ID =B.WIMBLEDON ) OR (A.PLAYER_ID =B.FR_OPEN) OR(A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN) OR (A.PLAYER_ID =B.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1

WITH T1 AS(SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T1.GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON T1.GAME = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH TB1 AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID,COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS W_NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN,COUNT(FR_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN,COUNT(US_OPEN) AS S_NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN,COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS A_NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(W_NUM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS RIGHT JOIN TB1 ON PLAYER_ID = ID GROUP BY ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT TEMP.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP JOIN PLAYERS P ON TEMP.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TEMP.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT TEMP.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON TEMP.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TEMP.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) ONE_GS_COUNT, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) ONE_GS_COUNT, 'FR_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) ONE_GS_COUNT, 'US_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) ONE_GS_COUNT, 'AU_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(ONE_GS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT ID, COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS A GROUP BY ID ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN TEMP ON P.PLAYER_ID=TEMP.ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN TEMP ON P.PLAYER_ID = TEMP.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS NUM_TOURNAMENT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS NUM_TOURNAMENT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS NUM_TOURNAMENT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS NUM_TOURNAMENT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(NUM_TOURNAMENT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, WCNT AS CNT FROM PLAYERS AS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON, COUNT(YEAR) AS WCNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) AS W ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, FCNT AS CNT FROM PLAYERS AS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT FR_OPEN, COUNT(YEAR) AS FCNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) AS W ON PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, UCNT AS CNT FROM PLAYERS AS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT US_OPEN, COUNT(YEAR) AS UCNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) AS W ON PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, ACNT AS CNT FROM PLAYERS AS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT AU_OPEN, COUNT(YEAR) AS ACNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) AS W ON PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN CNT IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE CNT END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TEMP.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS, TEMP WHERE PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = TEMP.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN TEMP ON P.PLAYER_ID = TEMP.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN TEMP T ON T.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT TEMP.ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TEMP.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON TEMP.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TEMP.ID

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP , PLAYERS WHERE TEMP.WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID GROUP BY WIMBLEDON

WITH TEMP AS( SELECT WINNER, COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON AS GAME', WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN AS GAME', FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN AS GAME', US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN AS GAME', AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS K GROUP BY WINNER ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN TEMP AS T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.WINNER

WITH TEMP AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TEMP AS( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' COL, WIMBLEDON VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' COL, FR_OPEN VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' COL, US_OPEN VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' COL, AU_OPEN VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT TEMP.VALUE AS PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TEMP.VALUE) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON TEMP.VALUE=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TEMP.VALUE ORDER BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP1 AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GRAND_SLAMS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN TEMP1 ON PLAYER_ID = GRAND_SLAMS GROUP BY 1

WITH TEMP_TABLE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_NAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP_TABLE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID = WINNER GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH TEMPTBL AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C2 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C3 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C4 ) SELECT GRANDSLAM AS PLAYER_ID ,P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMPTBL T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.GRANDSLAM = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT
