WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAM_PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS CHAM_PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS CHAM_PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS CHAM_PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT T2.PLAYER_ID, T2.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP T1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS T2 ON T1.CHAM_PLAYER_ID = T2.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN TMP ON PLAYER_ID = GAME GROUP BY 1, 2

WITH TMP AS (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS COMP, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR,'FR_OPEN' AS COMP, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR,'US_OPEN' AS COMP, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR,'AU_OPEN' AS COMP, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN TMP B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.WINNER GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TMP AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P LEFT JOIN TMP ON P.PLAYER_ID = TMP.WIN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING COUNT(WIN) >0

WITH TOTAL_WINS_PLAYER AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TOTAL_WINS_PLAYER GROUP BY PLAYER_ID)A JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID

WITH TOURNAMENT AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TOURNAMENT GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TOURNAMENTS AS ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS TOURNAMENT, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN TOURNAMENTS T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH W AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON ID , COUNT(1) AMOUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1), F AS (SELECT FR_OPEN ID , COUNT(1) AMOUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1), U AS (SELECT US_OPEN ID , COUNT(1) AMOUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1), A AS (SELECT AU_OPEN ID , COUNT(1) AMOUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1), ALL1 AS (SELECT * FROM W UNION ALL SELECT * FROM F UNION ALL SELECT * FROM U UNION ALL SELECT * FROM A) SELECT ID PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(AMOUNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON ALL1.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH W AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), F AS (SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), U AS (SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), A AS (SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT * FROM W UNION ALL SELECT * FROM F UNION ALL SELECT * FROM U UNION ALL SELECT * FROM A) C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_NAME ORDER BY P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH W_WINS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS W_W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON ) , F_WINS AS ( SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS F_W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN ) , U_WINS AS ( SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS U_W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN ) , AU_WINS AS ( SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS A_W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) , WIN_COUNT AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, IFNULL(W_WINS.W_W,0) AS WW, IFNULL(F_WINS.F_W,0) AS FW, IFNULL(U_WINS.U_W,0) AS UW, IFNULL(AU_WINS.A_W,0) AS AW FROM PLAYERS LEFT JOIN W_WINS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = W_WINS.ID LEFT JOIN F_WINS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = F_WINS.ID LEFT JOIN U_WINS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = U_WINS.ID LEFT JOIN AU_WINS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = AU_WINS.ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, WW + FW + UW + AW AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WIN_COUNT WHERE WW >0 OR FW >0 OR UW >0 OR AW >0

WITH WIMB AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT WIMB.PLAYER_ID, WIMB.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMB.TITLES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WIMB GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH WIMB AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT W.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WIMB W, PLAYERS P WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = W.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY W.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH WIMBLEDON AS (SELECT P.*, 'WIMBLEDON' FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.WIMBLEDON), FR AS (SELECT P.*, 'FR_OPEN' FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.FR_OPEN), AU AS (SELECT P.*, 'AU_OPEN' FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.AU_OPEN), US AS (SELECT P.*, 'US_OPEN' FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.US_OPEN), ALL_CHAMP AS ( SELECT * FROM WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT * FROM FR UNION ALL SELECT * FROM AU UNION ALL SELECT * FROM US ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL_CHAMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH WIMBLEDON AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON), FR_OPEN AS( SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN), US_OPEN AS( SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN), AU_OPEN AS( SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN), TOTAL_WINS_PLAYER AS( SELECT * FROM WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT * FROM FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM AU_OPEN ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TOTAL_WINS_PLAYER GROUP BY PLAYER_ID)A JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID

WITH WIN AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ORDER BY PLAYER_ID, YEAR) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WIN AS A LEFT OUTER JOIN PLAYERS AS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH WIN_OCC AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN WIN_OCC ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = WIN_OCC.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH WINNER AS ( SELECT WINNER, COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, 'W' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'F' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'U' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'A' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS A GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT A.*, B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN WINNER B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.WINNER

WITH WINNERS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNERS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH WINS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN WINS ON C = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH WINS AS ( SELECT DISTINCT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY WIMBLEDON) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY FR_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT US_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY US_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY AU_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT W.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(W.WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINS W, PLAYERS P WHERE W.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY W.PLAYER, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH WINTABLE AS( (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN WINTABLE ON PLAYER_ID = ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH ALL_WINS AS (SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN ALL_WINS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = ALL_WINS.CHAMP_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.WIN AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=CTE.WIN GROUP BY CTE.WIN

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENT, 'W' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'FR' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'US' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'AU' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT TOURNAMENT AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(LABEL) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.TOURNAMENT = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1 HAVING COUNT(LABEL) > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WON_THAT_YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + (PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + (PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + (PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS WON_THAT_YEAR FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE (PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + (PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + (PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + (PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) > 0 ) AS TALLY GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN TEMP T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SUB GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CTE.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, NEW_T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) AS W GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) AS NEW_T ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = NEW_T.PLAYER_ID

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT ID PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME ,SUM(C) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP JOIN PLAYERS ON TMP.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ID

SELECT TEMP.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TEMP JOIN PLAYERS ON TEMP.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRANDSLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , TITLE_COUNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT GRANDSLAM , COUNT(*) AS TITLE_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1) X LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON X.GRANDSLAM = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH C AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID IN (C.WIMBLEDON, C.FR_OPEN, C.US_OPEN, C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME,B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN ( SELECT ID,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS B GROUP BY ID ) AS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.ID

WITH TB1 AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT TB1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TB1.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TB1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.TOURNAMENT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS C JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON C.TOURNAMENT = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH WIN AS (SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN WIN W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.PLAYER GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT CHAMPIONSHIPS.YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT CHAMPIONSHIPS.YEAR, FR_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT CHAMPIONSHIPS.YEAR, US_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT CHAMPIONSHIPS.YEAR, AU_OPEN AS CHAMP_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.CHAMP_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.CHAMP_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH ALL_WINNER AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ALL_WINNER A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.WINNER GROUP BY 1

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON,1,0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN,1,0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN,1,0) +IF(P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN,1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.WIMBLEDON=B.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.FR_OPEN=B.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.US_OPEN=B.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.AU_OPEN=B.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT CHAMPIONS AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CHAMPIONS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPIONS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS CHAMPIONS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS CHAMPIONS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS CHAMPIONS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) D JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = D.CHAMPIONS GROUP BY CHAMPIONS

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN (SELECT T.ID, COUNT(1) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T GROUP BY T.ID) C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TOURNAMENT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS TOURNAMENT, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C_UNPIVOT ON P.PLAYER_ID = C_UNPIVOT.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PID AS PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME, A.CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PID, SUM(CNT) AS CNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PID, COUNT(1) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PID, COUNT(1) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PID, COUNT(1) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PID, COUNT(1) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) AS A GROUP BY PID) AS A INNER JOIN PLAYERS AS B ON A.PID = B.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) P JOIN PLAYERS ON P.PLAYER_ID=PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C4) TBL JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = TBL.WINNER GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) C ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID =US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT DISTINCT B.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY B.PLAYER_ID

SELECT * FROM( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1,2) T WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT C.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS) T WHERE T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT <> 0

WITH T1 AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS W_CHAMPION, COUNT(*) AS W_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON), T2 AS( SELECT FR_OPEN AS F_CHAMPION, COUNT(*) AS F_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN), T3 AS( SELECT US_OPEN AS U_CHAMPION, COUNT(*) AS U_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN), T4 AS( SELECT AU_OPEN AS A_CHAMPION, COUNT(*) AS A_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN), T5 AS( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, IFNULL(T1.W_COUNT,0)+IFNULL(T2.F_COUNT,0)+IFNULL(T3.U_COUNT,0)+IFNULL(T4.A_COUNT,0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT OUTER JOIN T1 ON (P.PLAYER_ID=T1.W_CHAMPION) LEFT OUTER JOIN T2 ON (P.PLAYER_ID=T2.F_CHAMPION) LEFT OUTER JOIN T3 ON (P.PLAYER_ID=T3.U_CHAMPION) LEFT OUTER JOIN T4 ON (P.PLAYER_ID=T4.A_CHAMPION)) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T5 WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT<>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(IF(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID,1,0)) + SUM(IF(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID,1,0)) + SUM(IF(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID,1,0)) + SUM(IF(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID,1,0))) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH NEW AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID,SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) A GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,B.PLAYER_NAME,GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM NEW A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE1 AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT * FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON, 1, 0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME) AS A WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CTE AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID GROUP BY C.ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH ALL_RECORD AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WINNER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ALL_RECORD A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.WINNER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH T AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS) A WHERE A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

WITH UNION_CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), PLAYER_WIN_COUNT_CTE AS( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM UNION_CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME , GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN PLAYER_WIN_COUNT_CTE PC ON P.PLAYER_ID = PC.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN (SELECT PLAYER, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER) AS T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER

WITH WINNINGS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN WINNINGS W ON W.WIN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME , SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END+CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH IDS AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM IDS JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID=IDS.ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT A.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH TOURNAMENT_PLAYER_DETAILS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS ENTRY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS ENTRY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS ENTRY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS ENTRY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), TOURNAMENTS_WON_PER_PLAYER AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID , COUNT(ENTRY) AS TOURNAMENTS_WON FROM TOURNAMENT_PLAYER_DETAILS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT TWPP.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , TWPP.TOURNAMENTS_WON AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TOURNAMENTS_WON_PER_PLAYER TWPP , PLAYERS P WHERE TWPP.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

WITH CTE AS (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS(SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAY FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C.PLAY AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.PLAY) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAY = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT * FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1, 2 ) A WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.GAME=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT TEMP.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TEMP.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON TEMP.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TEMP.PLAYER_ID

SELECT S1.PLAYER_ID, S2.PLAYER_NAME, S1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1) S1 INNER JOIN PLAYERS S2 ON S1.PLAYER_ID = S2.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(NUM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN TMP ON TMP.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 1

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT T.ID PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH A AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN VALUE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT A.VALUE AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A GROUP BY A.VALUE ) B LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON B.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, WINS_BY_ID.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(WIN_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) T GROUP BY 1 ) AS WINS_BY_ID JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = WINS_BY_ID.PLAYER_ID

WITH A AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,C.YEAR UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,C.YEAR UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.US_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,C.YEAR UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,C.YEAR ) SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , SUM(X1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A WHERE CASE WHEN X1 =0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) , TEMP2 AS ( SELECT PLAYER, COUNT(PLAYER) AS CNT FROM TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, B.CNT GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A LEFT JOIN TEMP2 B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER WHERE B.PLAYER IS NOT NULL

WITH TEMP AS ( (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C2 ON P.PLAYER_ID = C2.FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C3 ON P.PLAYER_ID = C3.US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C4 ON P.PLAYER_ID = C4.AU_OPEN) ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,A.PLAYER_NAME,A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, ( SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) +SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS) A WHERE A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

WITH CTE AS ( (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS TEMP ON TEMP.GS = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P1.PLAYER_ID, P1.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P2.GC) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P1 JOIN ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GC FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GC FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GC FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GC FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) P2 ON P1.PLAYER_ID = P2.GC GROUP BY 1, 2

WITH GRANDSLAMS AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( IF(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT * FROM GRANDSLAMS WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH T AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, NUM AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT ID, COUNT(ID) AS NUM FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)SUB GROUP BY 1)SUB1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = SUB1.ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GRAND_SLAM, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GRAND_SLAM, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME) T WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN =PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT X.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS X JOIN PLAYERS P ON X.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY X.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(FR_OPEN) WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(US_OPEN) WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(AU_OPEN) WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ) A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C WHERE 1=1 GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) OR (P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) OR (P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) OR (P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH TMP1 AS( SELECT *, 1 AS NUM FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS TMP) SELECT DISTINCT B.PLAYER_ID,B.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(NUM) OVER(PARTITION BY ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP1 AS A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS B ON A.ID=B.PLAYER_ID

WITH CHAMPS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPS AS C JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH TMP AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) + IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) TOTAL FROM PLAYERS , CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT TMP.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TOTAL) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON TMP.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING SUM(TOTAL) > 0

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A LEFT OUTER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT V.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C )V(PLAYER_ID) JOIN PLAYERS P ON V.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY V.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME HAVING COUNT(1) > 0

SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID

WITH RECORD AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT GAME PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM RECORD INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON GAME=PLAYER_ID GROUP BY GAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C, PLAYERS P GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAM_PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.GRAND_SLAM_PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GRAND_SLAM_PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.GRAND_SLAM_PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.GRAND_SLAM_PLAYER, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.GS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.GS = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY B.PLAYER_NAME

WITH T1 AS (SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,SUM(A.TOTAL) AS TOTAL FROM(SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) A GROUP BY 1) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,T1.TOTAL AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) T GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1, 2 HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0

WITH DATA AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT D.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(D.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM DATA D JOIN PLAYERS P ON D.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY D.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT CHAMPIONS.PLAYER_ID, CHAMPIONS.PLAYER_NAME, CHAMPIONS.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, ( (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE CHAMPIONSHIPS.WIMBLEDON = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE CHAMPIONSHIPS.FR_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE CHAMPIONSHIPS.US_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE CHAMPIONSHIPS.AU_OPEN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS ) AS CHAMPIONS WHERE CHAMPIONS.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(B.WIMBLEDON = A.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(B.FR_OPEN = A.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(B.US_OPEN = A.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(B.AU_OPEN = A.PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A, CHAMPIONSHIPS B GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT X.PLAYER_ID, X.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CW) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS CW FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS CF FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS CU FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS CA FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY AU_OPEN) X GROUP BY X.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CTE ON CTE.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON WINNERS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN WINNERS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN WINNERS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN WINNERS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, T1.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T2.WINNERS) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS T1 JOIN CTE T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.WINNERS GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM((CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON GROUP BY PLAYER_NAME

WITH MEDALSWON AS ( (SELECT WIMBLEDON WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) ) SELECT MEDALSWON.WINNER PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(MEDALSWON.WINNER) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM MEDALSWON JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID = MEDALSWON.WINNER GROUP BY WINNER

WITH CHAMPION AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPION C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WINNER GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN ( SELECT USER_ID, COUNT(USER_ID) AS CNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS USER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS USER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS USER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS USER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T3 GROUP BY USER_ID ) C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.USER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON ) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID , COUNT(FR_OPEN ) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID , COUNT(US_OPEN ) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN ) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , SUM(CT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = ID GROUP BY 1

WITH A AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS MEDALS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS MEDALS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS MEDALS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS MEDALS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT MEDALS_WON AS PLAYER_ID , B.PLAYER_NAME ,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A JOIN PLAYERS B ON B.PLAYER_ID = A.MEDALS_WON GROUP BY MEDALS_WON

SELECT T.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.WINNER GROUP BY WINNER ORDER BY PLAYER_ID DESC

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH AA AS ( SELECT AB.TT, SUM(AB.C) AS TOTAL_WON FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TT, COUNT(*) AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TT, COUNT(*) AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TT, COUNT(*) AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TT, COUNT(*) AS C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) AB GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, (B.TOTAL_WON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A LEFT JOIN AA B ON A. PLAYER_ID = B.TT HAVING B.TOTAL_WON IS NOT NULL

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)+ IF(FR_OPEN =PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)+ IF(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)+ IF(AU_OPEN =PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CHAMPIONSHIPS.WIMBLEDON OR PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CHAMPIONSHIPS.FR_OPEN OR PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CHAMPIONSHIPS.US_OPEN OR PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CHAMPIONSHIPS.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING COUNT(YEAR) > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, ( SUM(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH PC AS( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON, 1, 0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS GSW FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GSW) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PC GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT G.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(G.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM(SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS G JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = G.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY G.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT X.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) X JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT DISTINCT T1.PLAYER_ID, T2.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T1.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T1 JOIN PLAYERS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT ASC

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN)+ SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, ( SUM((WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) + (FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + (US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + (AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID)) ) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(W) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS W FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS W FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS W FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS W FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID )A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ), T2 AS( SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(C) C FROM T1 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT T2.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME , T2.C GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T2 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T2.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH T AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.GAME = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT F.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, F.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT * FROM PLAYERS AS P RIGHT JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS A ON A.ID = P.PLAYER_ID) AS F GROUP BY F.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS(SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP JOIN PLAYERS P ON TEMP.WIN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON ID, COUNT(*) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN ID, COUNT(*) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN ID, COUNT(*) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN ID, COUNT(*) CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) T JOIN PLAYERS ON T.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(B.WIMBLEDON=A.PLAYER_ID)+SUM(B.FR_OPEN =A.PLAYER_ID) +SUM(B.US_OPEN =A.PLAYER_ID)+SUM(B.AU_OPEN =A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A, CHAMPIONSHIPS B WHERE A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN OR A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CTE ON P.PLAYER_ID=CTE.ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P1.*, T2. GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P1 LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT GAME AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T1 GROUP BY GAME ) T2 ON P1.PLAYER_ID = T2.PLAYER_ID WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT IS NOT NULL

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID= FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID= US_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID= AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID= FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID= US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID= AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER GROUP BY PLAYER

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS MEDEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS MEDEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS MEDEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS MEDEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(MEDEL) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN T ON P.PLAYER_ID=T.MEDEL GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ORDER BY YEAR ASC ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GAMES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.GAMES GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CTE C ON C.GS = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT ALL_WINS FROM ( SELECT C1.WIMBLEDON AS ALL_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C1 UNION ALL SELECT C2.FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C2 UNION ALL SELECT C3.US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C3 UNION ALL SELECT C4.AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C4) AS NEW_TABLE) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TEMP.ALL_WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON TEMP.ALL_WINS = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TEMP.ALL_WINS

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT G.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS G GROUP BY G.PLAYER_ID) AS TEMP JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = TEMP.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GAMES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER, COUNT(1) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR,WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(1) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR,FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(1) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR,US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(1) AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR,AU_OPEN )A INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS UID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS UID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS UID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS UID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT UID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON T.UID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT DISTINCT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID)+SUM(C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)+SUM(C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)+SUM(C.AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH WIMBLEDON AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ), FR_OPEN AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ), US_OPEN AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ), AU_OPEN AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME ), CTE AS (SELECT * FROM WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT * FROM FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH BASE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT B.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(B.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM BASE B JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY B.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

WITH C AS (SELECT PID,COUNT(PID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A GROUP BY PID) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN C ON PLAYER_ID = C.PID

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) T WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS ( (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) ) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=CTE.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY CTE.PLAYER_ID DESC

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.TITLE GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH WINS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINS T1 INNER JOIN PLAYERS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN) T GROUP BY 1,2

WITH WIMBLEDON_COUNTS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON ), FROPEN_COUNTS AS ( SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN ), USOPEN_COUNTS AS ( SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN ), AU_OPEN AS ( SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ), UNION_WINS AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(COUNT_WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT * FROM WIMBLEDON_COUNTS UNION ALL SELECT * FROM FROPEN_COUNTS UNION ALL SELECT * FROM USOPEN_COUNTS UNION ALL SELECT * FROM AU_OPEN ) T1 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A LEFT JOIN UNION_WINS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT IS NOT NULL

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.ID GROUP BY 1,2
