WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAY, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAY, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAY, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAY, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT CTE.PLAY AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CTE.NUM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.PLAY = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.PLAY

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT DISTINCT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER=PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

WITH ALL_TITLES (PLAYER_ID) AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT ALL_TITLES.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ALL_TITLES.PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL_TITLES LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON ALL_TITLES.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ALL_TITLES.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE1 AS(SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPIONS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE1.CHAMPIONS GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT COUNT(1) AS SLAMS_COUNT, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(1) AS SLAMS_COUNT, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(1) AS SLAMS_COUNT, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(1) AS SLAMS_COUNT, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) A LEFT OUTER JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH WINS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINS W INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

WITH RES AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT R.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM RES R JOIN PLAYERS P USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A LEFT JOIN CTE B ON A. PLAYER_ID = B.ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING COUNT(B.ID)> 0

SELECT TBL.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) TBL INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON TBL.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY TBL.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE ON P.PLAYER_ID=CTE.WIN GROUP BY 1

WITH A AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT C.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.GRAND_SLAMS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.GRAND_SLAMS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C, PLAYERS P GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH A AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME ,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID WHERE A.PLAYER_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A JOIN PLAYERS B ON B.PLAYER_ID = A.TOURNAMENT GROUP BY B.PLAYER_ID

WITH A AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID,C.YEAR UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,C.YEAR UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.US_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,C.YEAR UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ,C.YEAR ) SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , SUM(X1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A WHERE CASE WHEN X1 =0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = PLAYER GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GS, WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GS, FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GS, US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GS, AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON B.PLAYER_ID = A.ID GROUP BY A.ID, B.PLAYER_NAME

WITH WINNING_IDS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, T2.PLAYER_NAME, T1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNING_IDS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) T1 INNER JOIN PLAYERS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T2.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) TMP GROUP BY 1) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT R.PLAYER_ID,R.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN) UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN) UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN))R GROUP BY R.PLAYER_ID

SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T JOIN PLAYERS ON T.WIMBLEDON = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY WIMBLEDON

WITH B AS ((SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(B.WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.WIN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME

WITH A AS (SELECT * FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS ORDER BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, YEAR), B AS (SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, A.YEAR, IF(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON,1,0)+IF(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN,1,0)+IF(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN,1,0)+IF(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN,1,0) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM B GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT)>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS RIGHT JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.ID GROUP BY ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH GRAND_SLAM AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS TOURNEY_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS TOURNEY_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS TOURNEY_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS TOURNEY_CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(TOURNEY_CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM GRAND_SLAM G LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON G.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID WHERE P.PLAYER_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.GRAND_SLAM = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT Q1.PLAYER_ID, PL.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(MATCHES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS MATCHES FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )PV GROUP BY 1 )Q1 JOIN PLAYERS PL ON PL.PLAYER_ID = Q1.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) AS W WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TOTAL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), CTE2 AS ( SELECT TOTAL AS ID,COUNT(*) AS WIN_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY TOTAL ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,CTE2.WIN_COUNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE2 ON P.PLAYER_ID=CTE2.ID

WITH CTE1 AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GAMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GAMES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE1.GAMES = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID,1,0))+ SUM(IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0))+ SUM(IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0))+ SUM(IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS) AS T WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT >0

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GRAND FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GRAND FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GRAND FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID= FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID= US_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID= AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID= FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID= US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID= AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS(SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(T.CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) T JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ( SELECT PLAYER_ID,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS )X GROUP BY PLAYER_ID)X ON P.PLAYER_ID=X.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT ID, COUNT(1) CNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID , B.PLAYER_NAME , CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 A , PLAYERS B WHERE A.ID = PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WINNER GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS P1 ON P.PLAYER_ID = P1.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS P2 ON P.PLAYER_ID = P2.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS P3 ON P.PLAYER_ID = P3.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS P4 ON P.PLAYER_ID = P4.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1) TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) AS T JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON T.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(YEAR) AS COUNT_WINS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) (SELECT P.*, SUM(C.COUNT_WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2)

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(NUM_SLAMS) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) NUM_SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(FR_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(US_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(AU_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1 ) T GROUP BY 1

WITH C AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID =C.WIN GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT A.YEAR, A.WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS A UNION ALL SELECT B.YEAR, B.FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS B UNION ALL SELECT C.YEAR, C.US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT D.YEAR, D.AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS D) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ORDER BY PLAYER_ID DESC

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) GS ON GS.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C ON PLAYER_ID = C.PID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), CTE1 AS( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF (PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON,1,0)) + SUM(IF (PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN,1,0)) + SUM(IF (PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN,1,0)) + SUM(IF (PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN,1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, T2.COUNTS AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN ( SELECT ID, COUNT(*) AS COUNTS FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T1 GROUP BY ID ) T2 ON T2.ID = PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P WHERE PLAYER_ID IN (WIMBLEDON, FR_OPEN, US_OPEN, AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT( *) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , 'WIMBLEDON' AS TOURNMENT, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 'FR_OPEN' AS TOURNMENT, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 'US_OPEN' AS TOURNMENT, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 'AU_OPEN' AS TOURNMENT, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (ONE+TWO+THREE+FOUR) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ONE, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TWO, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS THREE, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS B INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID=B.WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=B.FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=B.US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1 ) X GROUP BY 1

WITH WINNERS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN WINNERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH T1(WINNER) AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT NEWTABLE.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, NUM AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM T1 GROUP BY WINNER) AS NEWTABLE JOIN PLAYERS ON NEWTABLE.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( (C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID) + (C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + (C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + (C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) +SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) +SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS TB1 JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON TB1.PLAYER_ID= WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID =FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID =AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE_1 AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WIMBLEDON_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS FRENCH_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(US_OPEN) AS US_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2 UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS AU_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1,2) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE_1 GROUP BY 1

WITH T1 AS (SELECT DISTINCT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1), T2 AS (SELECT DISTINCT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1), T3 AS (SELECT DISTINCT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1), T4 AS (SELECT DISTINCT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COALESCE(T1.GAME,0)+COALESCE(T2.GAME,0)+COALESCE(T3.GAME,0)+COALESCE(T4.GAME,0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN T1 ON P.PLAYER_ID=T1.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN T2 ON P.PLAYER_ID=T2.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN T3 ON P.PLAYER_ID=T3.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN T4 ON P.PLAYER_ID=T4.PLAYER_ID WHERE COALESCE(T1.GAME,0)+COALESCE(T2.GAME,0)+COALESCE(T3.GAME,0)+COALESCE(T4.GAME,0)>0

WITH SLAMS AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM SLAMS JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID=SLAMS.SLAM GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER GROUP BY 1

WITH TBL_GRP AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS MATCH FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS MATCH FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS MATCH FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS MATCH FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.*,COUNT(B.MATCH) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN TBL_GRP B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.MATCH GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A ,PLAYERS B WHERE A.ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) T GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, 'WIMBLEDON' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'FR_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'US_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'AU_OPEN' AS TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(TOURNAMENT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH WIMBLEDON AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, WIMBLEDON AS C FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON ), FR_OPEN AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, FR_OPEN AS C FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN ), US_OPEN AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, US_OPEN AS C FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN ), AU_OPEN AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, AU_OPEN AS C FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ), CTE AS ( SELECT * FROM WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT * FROM FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ( SELECT T AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(T) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C2 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C3 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C4) T GROUP BY T) T2 ON T2.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS RIGHT JOIN (SELECT ID, COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS SUBQUERY GROUP BY ID) SUBQUERY ON SUBQUERY.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

SELECT B.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT J.GS, COUNT(J.YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) J GROUP BY 1) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.GS = B.PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS FIELD, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS FIELD, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS FIELD, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS FIELD, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T1.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T1.WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) + SUM(IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) + SUM(IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1,0)) + SUM(IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS) T WHERE T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), CTE2 AS (SELECT ID, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM CTE GROUP BY ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, CTE2.NUM AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE2 JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE2.ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS WHERE (SELECT SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) != 0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH C AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN GS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GS) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN C ON PLAYER_ID=GS GROUP BY 1

WITH TMP AS (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.US_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP GROUP BY 1

SELECT B.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,SUM(A.GAME_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GAME_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS GAME_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS GAME_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS GAME_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN )A GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID )B JOIN PLAYERS P ON B.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID WHERE B.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

WITH TOTAL AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS C, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS C, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS C, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS C, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS W FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN)) SELECT C AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(W) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TOTAL JOIN PLAYERS ON TOTAL.C = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT <> 0

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.*, COUNT(C.WINNER) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WINNER GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P RIGHT JOIN (SELECT TOURNAMENT AS PLAYER, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENT, 'WIMBLEDON' AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'FRENCH' AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'US' AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'AUSTRALIAN' AS SLAM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T GROUP BY PLAYER ) AS T ON P.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM( (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) )GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

WITH C1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C1.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C1.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON C1.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) U GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) W USING (PLAYER_ID)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), WINNERS AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, W.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNERS W JOIN PLAYERS P ON W.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(A.WINS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WINS ,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS WINS ,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(US_OPEN) AS WINS ,US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS WINS ,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=A.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH ALL_WINNER AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ALL_WINNER A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.WINNER GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C, PLAYERS P WHERE PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN, 1, 0) + IF(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON ( PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN ) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT X.PLAYER_ID, X.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(X.WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ) X GROUP BY X.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS(SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP JOIN PLAYERS P ON TEMP.WIN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS SCORES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T1.SCORES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.SCORES = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN)AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID IN (C.WIMBLEDON, C.FR_OPEN, C.US_OPEN, C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), CTE1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH PLAYER_WIN_CT AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYER_WIN_CT WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A ON PLAYER_ID = A.WINNER GROUP BY WINNER HAVING COUNT(WINNER)>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN, 1, 0)) + SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN, 1, 0))) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT SUM(IF(WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) + SUM(IF(FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) + SUM(IF(US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID, 1,0)) + SUM(IF(AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID,1,0)) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS) T WHERE T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT <> 0

WITH A AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS CT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(CT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIN, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TEMP GROUP BY WIN ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, B.CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN CTE B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIN

WITH WON AS ( SELECT ID, COUNT(ID) AS CNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, W.CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN WON W ON W.ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CTE ON PLAYER_ID=CTE.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH TOURNAMENT_PLAYER_DETAILS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS TOURNAMENTS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS TOURNAMENTS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS TOURNAMENTS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , 1 AS TOURNAMENTS_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), TOURNAMENTS_WON_PER_PLAYER AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID , COUNT(TOURNAMENTS_WON) AS TOURNAMENTS_WON FROM TOURNAMENT_PLAYER_DETAILS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT TWPP.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , TWPP.TOURNAMENTS_WON AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TOURNAMENTS_WON_PER_PLAYER TWPP , PLAYERS P WHERE TWPP.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH A AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.US_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) AS X1 FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID , PLAYER_NAME , SUM(X1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM A WHERE CASE WHEN X1 =0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH GRANDSLAM_WINNERS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TITLES) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM GRANDSLAM_WINNERS JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM((WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID) + (FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + (US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) + (AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID)) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID IN (WIMBLEDON, FR_OPEN, US_OPEN, AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT DISTINCT WIN AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT C.WIMBLEDON AS WIN, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT C.FR_OPEN AS WIN, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT C.US_OPEN AS WIN, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT C.AU_OPEN AS WIN , P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) AS T GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS CNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN TMP ON TMP.ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C. PLAYER_ID, P. PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON C. PLAYER_ID =P. PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C. PLAYER_ID, P. PLAYER_NAME

WITH WINNERS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNERS W LEFT OUTER JOIN PLAYERS P ON W.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(C.WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID, 1,0) + IF(C.FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID, 1,0) + IF(C.US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID, 1,0) + IF(C.AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID, 1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID IN (C.WIMBLEDON, C.FR_OPEN, C.US_OPEN, C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAM_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAM_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME

WITH PLAYER_CHAMPIONSHIPS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), PLAYER_WINS AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYER_CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PW.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, PW.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYER_WINS PW LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON PW.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY 1

SELECT A.PID PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CW) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON PID, COUNT(YEAR) CW FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PID, COUNT(YEAR) CW FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PID, COUNT(YEAR) CW FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PID, COUNT(YEAR) CW FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.PID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT PA.PLAYER_ID, PA.PLAYER_NAME, A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, SUM( IF(C.WIMBLEDON=P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) +IF(C.FR_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) +IF(C.US_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0) +IF(C.AU_OPEN=P.PLAYER_ID, 1, 0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) A JOIN PLAYERS PA ON A.PLAYER_ID=PA.PLAYER_ID WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT!=0 ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT

WITH CTE AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)), NUM AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1) SELECT NUM.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM NUM JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID=NUM.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON + FRENCH_OPEN + US_OPEN + AUS_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.*, C.YEAR, CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS WIMBLEDON, CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS FRENCH_OPEN, CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS US_OPEN, CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS AUS_OPEN FROM PLAYERS AS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ORDER BY PLAYER_ID) AS T GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) P JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P1.PLAYER_ID, P1.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P1.PLAYER_ID =C1.WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(P1.PLAYER_ID =C1.FR_OPEN)+SUM(P1.PLAYER_ID =C1.US_OPEN)+ SUM(P1.PLAYER_ID =C1.AU_OPEN)AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P1 JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 ON P1.PLAYER_ID = C1.WIMBLEDON OR P1.PLAYER_ID = C1.FR_OPEN OR P1.PLAYER_ID = C1.US_OPEN OR P1.PLAYER_ID = C1.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P1.PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN T1 USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CHAMPIONSHIPS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.*, COUNT(TMP.ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN TMP ON P.PLAYER_ID=TMP.ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING COUNT(TMP.ID) <> 0

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.WINNER GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, 'WIMBLEDON' AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'FR_OPEN' AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'US_OPEN' AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 'AU_OPEN' AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.TITLE) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID,B.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( (SELECT YEAR,WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON THEN WIMBLEDON ELSE OTHER END AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR) UNION (SELECT YEAR,FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN FR_OPEN THEN FR_OPEN ELSE OTHER END AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR) UNION (SELECT YEAR,US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN US_OPEN THEN US_OPEN ELSE OTHER END AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR) UNION (SELECT YEAR,AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN AU_OPEN THEN AU_OPEN ELSE OTHER END AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY YEAR) ) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH L AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT L.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM L LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, T.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) AS T GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(X.T) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS T FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) X ON P.PLAYER_ID= X.T GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, ( COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 END) + COUNT(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 END) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON (P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) P GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH T AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON CHA, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN CHA, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN CHA, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN CHA, COUNT(*) C FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ), T1 AS( SELECT CHA, SUM(C) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T GROUP BY CHA ) SELECT T1.CHA PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME , T1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.CHA=P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CHAMPIONSHIPS_FLATTENED AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CF.WINNER AS PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(CF.WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS_FLATTENED AS CF JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON CF.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CF.WINNER, P.PLAYER_NAME HAVING COUNT(CF.WINNER) > 0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A JOIN PLAYERS P ON (A.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH UNIONED AS ( SELECT C1.WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 UNION ALL SELECT C2.FR_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C2 UNION ALL SELECT C3.US_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C3 UNION ALL SELECT C4.AU_OPEN AS CHAMP FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C4) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CHAMP) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN UNIONED ON P.PLAYER_ID = UNIONED.CHAMP GROUP BY 1

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + SUM(C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID IN (C.WIMBLEDON, C.FR_OPEN, C.US_OPEN, C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH GRANDGAME AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT GAME AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM GRANDGAME LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID=GRANDGAME.GAME GROUP BY GAME

WITH NEW_TABLE AS ( SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS MATHC, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS MATHC, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS MATHC, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS MATHC, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM NEW_TABLE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH P AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN P B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS SLAMS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), TMP2 AS ( SELECT SLAMS AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT T2.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, T2.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TMP2 AS T2 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON T2.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP JOIN PLAYERS ON TEMP.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON, 1,0)) + SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN, 1,0)) + SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN, 1,0)) + SUM(IF(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN, 1,0)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT IS NOT NULL

SELECT A.WIN AS PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A LEFT OUTER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.WIN = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.WIN

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, A.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1 )A LEFT OUTER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T ON P.PLAYER_ID=T.WINNER GROUP BY T.WINNER

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYERID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYERID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYERID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYERID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYER_ID = PLAYERID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN YEAR THEN WIMBLEDON END AS TYPE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN YEAR THEN FR_OPEN END AS TYPE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN YEAR THEN US_OPEN END AS TYPE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID, CASE WHEN YEAR THEN AU_OPEN END AS TYPE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T. PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) WINS ON WINS.WINNER = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH GS AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TITLE FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT G.TITLE AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM GS G LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON G.TITLE=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CHAMPS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAMP, COUNT(YEAR) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS CHAMP, COUNT(YEAR) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS CHAMP, COUNT(YEAR) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS CHAMP, COUNT(YEAR) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(TIMES) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPS C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.CHAMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P ) T WHERE T.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM( (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON) + (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+ (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+ (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT >0

WITH PC AS( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, IF(C.WIMBLEDON IS NULL,0,1) AS GSW FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, IF(C.FR_OPEN IS NULL,0,1) AS GSW FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, IF(C.US_OPEN IS NULL,0,1) AS GSW FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, IF(C.AU_OPEN IS NULL,0,1) AS GSW FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) SELECT PC.PLAYER_ID, PC.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PC.GSW) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PC GROUP BY PC.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON WIN = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_NAME

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY COUNT(*)

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN TOURNAMENT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = TEMP.TOURNAMENT GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(PLAYER_ID)GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.TNT GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 ON P.PLAYER_ID=C1.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 ON P.PLAYER_ID=C1.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 ON P.PLAYER_ID=C1.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 ON P.PLAYER_ID=C1.AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENT, 'W' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'FR' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'US' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, 'AU' AS LABEL FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT TOURNAMENT AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.TOURNAMENT = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1 HAVING COUNT(LABEL) > 0

WITH PLAYER_SLAM_CNT AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(US_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID,COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLYR_CNT.PLAYER_ID, PLYR.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(PLYR_CNT.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYER_SLAM_CNT AS PLYR_CNT JOIN PLAYERS AS PLYR ON PLYR.PLAYER_ID = PLYR_CNT.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH PLAYER_WIN_CNT AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) X GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PL.PLAYER_ID, PL.PLAYER_NAME, PC.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS PL INNER JOIN PLAYER_WIN_CNT PC ON (PL.PLAYER_ID = PC.PLAYER_ID)

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID,'W' AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID,'F' AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID,'U' AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID,'A' AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.ID AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(GAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON CTE.ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH P AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM P LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON P.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+ SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN =PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN =PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1
