SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS USING (PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH WINS AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT W.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINS W JOIN PLAYERS P ON W.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH TBL AS ( SELECT PW.PLAYER_ID, PW.PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS PW RIGHT OUTER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON PW.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT OUTER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT OUTER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS P RIGHT OUTER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TBL GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(NUM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P, (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.WIMBLEDON) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C, PLAYERS AS P WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.FR_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C, PLAYERS AS P WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.US_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C, PLAYERS AS P WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.AU_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C, PLAYERS AS P WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) AS A WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN =PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COALESCE(C1, 0) + COALESCE(C2, 0) + COALESCE(C3, 0) + COALESCE(C4, 0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, COUNT(*) AS C1 FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS C2 FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) F ON P.PLAYER_ID = F.ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS C3 FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) U ON P.PLAYER_ID = U.ID LEFT JOIN (SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, COUNT(*) AS C4 FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.ID WHERE COALESCE(C1, 0) + COALESCE(C2, 0) + COALESCE(C3, 0) + COALESCE(C4, 0) > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN)+SUM(P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COALESCE((SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + SUM(CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS),0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT >0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS LEFT JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID IN (WIMBLEDON, FR_OPEN, US_OPEN, AU_OPEN) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT IS NOT NULL

WITH WINS AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ), WINS_PLAYER AS ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINS GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT T0.PLAYER_ID, T0.PLAYER_NAME, T1.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS T0 JOIN WINS_PLAYER T1 USING (PLAYER_ID)

WITH ALLCHAMPIONSHIPS AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM_WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(GRAND_SLAM_WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALLCHAMPIONSHIPS A,PLAYERS P WHERE A.GRAND_SLAM_WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH WI AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ), FR AS ( SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ), US AS ( SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ), AU AS ( SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) TIMES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, IFNULL(WI.TIMES,0) + IFNULL(FR.TIMES,0) + IFNULL(US.TIMES,0) + IFNULL(AU.TIMES,0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS LEFT JOIN WI ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = WI.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN FR ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = FR.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN US ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = US.PLAYER_ID LEFT JOIN AU ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = AU.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT != 0

WITH CHAMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMP C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

SELECT RESULT.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT SLAM AS PLAYER_ID, SUM(COUNTO) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS SLAM, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS COUNTO FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS SLAM, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS COUNTO FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS SLAM, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS COUNTO FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS SLAM, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS COUNTO FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) AGG GROUP BY SLAM) RESULT LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = RESULT.PLAYER_ID

SELECT TEMP2.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, TEMP2.CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) CNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) TEMP2 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON TEMP2.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID IN (WIMBLEDON, FR_OPEN, US_OPEN, AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH ALL_CHAMP AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), CHAMP_COUNT AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ALL_CHAMP GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMP_COUNT ON P.PLAYER_ID = CHAMP_COUNT.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, NEW_TABLE.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P INNER JOIN (SELECT PLAYER,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS TEMP GROUP BY PLAYER) AS NEW_TABLE ON P.PLAYER_ID=NEW_TABLE.PLAYER GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH T1 AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = T1.NAME GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) WINS FROM PLAYERS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WINS) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING SUM(WINS)>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) + (CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID OR C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID ) S GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CHAMPIONS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.CHAMPION) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONS C ON C.CHAMPION = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2 HAVING COUNT(C.CHAMPION) > 0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C1) + SUM(C2) + SUM(C3) + SUM(C4) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS C1, CASE WHEN FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS C2,CASE WHEN US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS C3,CASE WHEN AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS C4 FROM PLAYERS, CHAMPIONSHIPS ) P GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME HAVING SUM(C1) + SUM(C2) + SUM(C3) + SUM(C4) > 0

WITH ABC AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT ABC.ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ABC.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ABC JOIN PLAYERS P ON ABC.ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ABC.ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CTE.ID AS PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.ID = PLAYER_ID GROUP BY CTE.ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C. PLAYER_ID, P. PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C. PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON C. PLAYER_ID =P. PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C. PLAYER_ID, P. PLAYER_NAME

SELECT T.PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME,SUM(WIN_NUMBER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) AS WIN_NUMBER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(FR_OPEN) AS WIN_NUMBER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(US_OPEN) AS WIN_NUMBER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER, COUNT(AU_OPEN) AS WIN_NUMBER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) AS T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON T.PLAYER=PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.PLAYER ORDER BY SUM(WIN_NUMBER)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2 HAVING COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) > 0

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A JOIN PLAYERS P ON A.ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ID

WITH WIMBLEDON AS ( SELECT DISTINCT WIMBLEDON AS USER_ID,COUNT(YEAR) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON ), FR_OPEN AS ( SELECT DISTINCT FR_OPEN AS USER_ID,COUNT(YEAR) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN ), US_OPEN AS ( SELECT DISTINCT US_OPEN AS USER_ID,COUNT(YEAR) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN ), AU_OPEN AS ( SELECT DISTINCT AU_OPEN AS USER_ID,COUNT(YEAR) AS NUM FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN ), TOTAL AS ( SELECT * FROM WIMBLEDON UNION ALL SELECT * FROM FR_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM US_OPEN UNION ALL SELECT * FROM AU_OPEN ) SELECT USER_ID AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,SUM(NUM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TOTAL T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.USER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY USER_ID

WITH WINS AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID, 1 AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 1 AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 1 AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID, 1 AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT W.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(W.WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINS W INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_NAME, P.PLAYER_ID, C.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN ( SELECT CHAMPION, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) T GROUP BY CHAMPION ) C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.CHAMPION

SELECT TEMP.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) TEMP LEFT JOIN PLAYERS USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY 1 DESC

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CTE ON PLAYER_ID = WON GROUP BY 1

SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS T1, PLAYERS P WHERE T1.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T1.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT WIN AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.WIN=PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.FR_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.US_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME UNION ALL SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.AU_OPEN GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME )A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS CHAMPIONSHIP, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS CHAMPIONSHIP, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS CHAMPIONSHIP, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS CHAMPIONSHIP, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), CTE2 AS (SELECT PLAYER_ID, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE2 C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SELECT COUNT(WIMBLEDON) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID) +(SELECT COUNT(FR_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) +(SELECT COUNT(US_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID ) +(SELECT COUNT(AU_OPEN) FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS WHERE AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT <>0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING (GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0)

WITH W AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID, COUNT(WIMBLEDON) SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(FR_OPEN) SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) UNION ALL(SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(US_OPEN) SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID, COUNT(AU_OPEN) SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN)) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(W.SLAMS_COUNT) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN W ON P.PLAYER_ID=W.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY W.PLAYER_ID

WITH NEW AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT N.PLAYER_WON AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(N.PLAYER_WON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM NEW N JOIN PLAYERS P ON N.PLAYER_WON = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS A JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.CNT AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN (SELECT CHAMPION, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS CHAMPION FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T GROUP BY CHAMPION) C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.CHAMPION

WITH C AS ( SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(1) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(C.CHAM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM C LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY C.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0 ORDER BY P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CHAMP_LONG AS (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMP_LONG C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.WINNER = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH PERCOUNT AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PERCOUNT A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME,( SUM(P.PLAYER_ID= C.WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID IN (C.WIMBLEDON, C.FR_OPEN, C.US_OPEN, C.AU_OPEN) GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) CHAMP INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON CHAMP.WINNER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CTE C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT ST.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(ST.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) ST LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON ST.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ST.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID) SUB GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CHAM) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C1.WIMBLEDON) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C1 ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = C1.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C2.FR_OPEN) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C2 ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = C2.FR_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C3.US_OPEN) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C3 ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = C3.US_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C4.AU_OPEN) AS CHAM FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C4 ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = C4.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID) T GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH X AS ( SELECT YEAR,'WIMBLEDON' AS TITLE, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR,'FR_OPEN' AS TITLE, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR,'US_OPEN' AS TITLE, US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION SELECT YEAR,'AU_OPEN' AS TITLE, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM X LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON X.PLAYER = P.PLAYER_ID WHERE PLAYER_ID IS NOT NULL GROUP BY 1,2

WITH TITLES(GRAND_SLAM) AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT DISTINCT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(GRAND_SLAM) OVER (PARTITION BY PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS, TITLES WHERE PLAYER_ID = GRAND_SLAM

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(P.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON CTE.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS TOUR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.TOUR = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON T1.WINNER=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH RES AS ( (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS NO_OF_TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) UNION ALL (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS NO_OF_TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) UNION ALL (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS NO_OF_TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) UNION ALL (SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, COUNT(C.YEAR) AS NO_OF_TITLES FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID) ), AGG_RES AS ( SELECT RES.PLAYER_ID, SUM(NO_OF_TITLES) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM RES GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ) SELECT AGG_RES.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, AGG_RES.GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM AGG_RES JOIN PLAYERS ON AGG_RES.PLAYER_ID = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID AS PLAYER_ID , P.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME , SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN) + SUM(P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(A.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE A JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE AS C JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON C.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(FR_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID)+SUM(AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1 HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A LEFT JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY A.PLAYER_ID

(SELECT PLAYER_ID,SUM(GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID , COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY PLAYER_ID )A GROUP BY PLAYER_ID)B JOIN (SELECT * FROM PLAYERS)P ON P.PLAYER_ID=B.PLAYER_ID

SELECT C.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) C JOIN PLAYERS P USING(PLAYER_ID) GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS), CTE2 AS (SELECT ID, COUNT(*) AS COUNTS FROM CTE GROUP BY ID) SELECT C.ID AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, C.COUNTS AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE2 C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON C.ID = P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( (SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) UNION ALL (SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME FROM PLAYERS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) ) SELECT DISTINCT(PLAYER_ID), PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_NAME) OVER(PARTITION BY PLAYER_NAME) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE

WITH WINNERS AS ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS)) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WINNERS W JOIN PLAYERS P ON W.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN ( (SELECT YEAR, 'WIMBLEDON' AS GAME, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION (SELECT YEAR, 'FR_OPEN' AS GAME, FR_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION (SELECT YEAR, 'US_OPEN' AS GAME, US_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION (SELECT YEAR, 'AU_OPEN' AS GAME, AU_OPEN AS WINNER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) ) WINNERS ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = WINNERS.WINNER_ID GROUP BY PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP JOIN PLAYERS P ON ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.WON) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID = CTE.WON GROUP BY CTE.WON

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COALESCE(W.TITLES, 0) + COALESCE(F.TITLES, 0) + COALESCE(U.TITLES, 0) + COALESCE(A.TITLES, 0) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P LEFT JOIN (SELECT WIMBLEDON, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY WIMBLEDON) W ON P.PLAYER_ID = W.WIMBLEDON LEFT JOIN (SELECT FR_OPEN, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY FR_OPEN) F ON P.PLAYER_ID = F.FR_OPEN LEFT JOIN (SELECT US_OPEN, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY US_OPEN) U ON P.PLAYER_ID = U.US_OPEN LEFT JOIN (SELECT AU_OPEN, COUNT(*) TITLES FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY AU_OPEN) A ON P.PLAYER_ID = A.AU_OPEN WHERE COALESCE(W.TITLES, 0) + COALESCE(F.TITLES, 0) + COALESCE(U.TITLES, 0) + COALESCE(A.TITLES, 0) != 0

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GRAND_SLAM, YEAR FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.GRAND_SLAM = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH MATCHES AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN MATCHES M ON P.PLAYER_ID = M.GAME GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS GROUP BY 1) A WHERE GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE1 AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT T1.PLAYER_ID, T2.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T1.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 AS T1 JOIN PLAYERS T2 ON T1.PLAYER_ID=T2.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(WIMBLEDON + FRENCH_OPEN + US_OPEN + AUS_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT P.*, C.YEAR, CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS WIMBLEDON, CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS FRENCH_OPEN, CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS US_OPEN, CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS AUS_OPEN FROM PLAYERS AS P CROSS JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS AS C ORDER BY PLAYER_ID) AS T GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING SUM(WIMBLEDON + FRENCH_OPEN + US_OPEN + AUS_OPEN ) != 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID,P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN C.WIMBLEDON = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN C.FR_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN C.US_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)+ SUM(CASE WHEN C.AU_OPEN = P.PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS C CROSS JOIN PLAYERS P GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT > 0

WITH CTE AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS IDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS IDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS IDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS IDS FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT C.IDS AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.IDS) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE C INNER JOIN PLAYERS P ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.IDS GROUP BY C.IDS

WITH CTE AS( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID, A.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE INNER JOIN PLAYERS A ON CTE.PLAYER_ID = A.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT ID AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ((SELECT WIMBLEDON AS TOURNAMENT, WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT FR_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT US_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) UNION ALL (SELECT AU_OPEN AS TOURNAMENT, AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) )AS T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS AS P ON T.ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY ID

WITH T AS (SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS T1 LEFT JOIN T ON T1.PLAYER_ID = T.PLAYER GROUP BY PLAYER_ID HAVING GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT>0

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, (SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN)) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON OR PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN OR PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID=C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID=C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT ASC

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(YEAR) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS A LEFT JOIN (SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING COUNT(YEAR) > 0

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID = WIMBLEDON) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = FR_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = US_OPEN) + SUM(PLAYER_ID = AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID

SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, SUM(PLAYER_ID=WIMBLEDON)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID=FR_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID=US_OPEN)+ SUM(PLAYER_ID=AU_OPEN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS P, CHAMPIONSHIPS C WHERE P.PLAYER_ID = C.WIMBLEDON OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.FR_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.US_OPEN OR P.PLAYER_ID = C.AU_OPEN GROUP BY P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE1 AS( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C1.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE1 C1 JOIN PLAYERS P ON C1.PLAYER_ID=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME,COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS JOIN CTE ON PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID = CTE.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME

SELECT A.PLAYER_ID, B.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(1)AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS PPLAYER_IDID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) A INNER JOIN PLAYERS B ON A.PLAYER_ID = B.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM (SELECT WIMBLEDON FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) W LEFT JOIN PLAYERS A ON W.WIMBLEDON=A.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_NAME

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT CTE.PLAYER_ID,PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(CTE.PLAYER_ID) GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON CTE.PLAYER_ID=PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1

WITH T AS ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

SELECT WINNER AS PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WINNER) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM ( SELECT SUBQ.YEAR, SUBQ.WINNER, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME AS PLAYER_NAME FROM ( SELECT YEAR, WIMBLEDON AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, FR_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, US_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR, AU_OPEN AS WINNER FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) AS SUBQ LEFT JOIN PLAYERS ON SUBQ.WINNER = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID) AS SUBQ2 GROUP BY PLAYER_ID ORDER BY GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT DESC

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS GAME FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T.GAME AS PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(*) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM TEMP T LEFT JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.GAME=P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH WIN AS ( SELECT YEAR , WIMBLEDON AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR , FR_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR , US_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT YEAR , AU_OPEN AS WIN FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID, PLAYERS.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(WIN.WIN) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM WIN INNER JOIN PLAYERS ON WIN.WIN = PLAYERS.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY 1,2

WITH T AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN PLAYER_ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS) SELECT T.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(T.PLAYER_ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM T JOIN PLAYERS P ON T.PLAYER_ID = P.PLAYER_ID GROUP BY T.PLAYER_ID

SELECT PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN FR_OPEN= PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS INNER JOIN CHAMPIONSHIPS ON WIMBLEDON = PLAYER_ID OR FR_OPEN= PLAYER_ID OR US_OPEN=PLAYER_ID OR AU_OPEN=PLAYER_ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME

WITH CHAMP AS ( SELECT WIMBLEDON AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT FR_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT US_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS UNION ALL SELECT AU_OPEN AS ID FROM CHAMPIONSHIPS ) SELECT P.PLAYER_ID, P.PLAYER_NAME, COUNT(C.ID) AS GRAND_SLAMS_COUNT FROM PLAYERS AS P RIGHT JOIN CHAMP C ON P.PLAYER_ID = C.ID GROUP BY PLAYER_ID, PLAYER_NAME
